  "intent_precise": "Purification of Genomic DNA: Using magplate (deep_well_plate, slot Deep Well Plate), Final Plate (pcr_plate, slot 1), Reservoir (reservoir, slot 7). With magnetic module. (1) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1). (2) Mix 5 times at 200\u00b5L. (3) Incubate for 20 minutes. (4) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (5) Mix 10 times at 50\u00b5L. (6) Transfer 6\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (7) Mix 5 times at 50\u00b5L. (8) Engage magnets for bead separation. (9) Incubate for 5 minutes. (10) Distribute 100\u00b5L from source A1 to destination wells A1-A1 (4 wells). (11) Incubate for 1 minutes. (12) Transfer 100\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (13) Incubate for 2 minutes. (14) Disengage magnets to release beads. (15) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (16) Mix 5 times at 30\u00b5L. (17) Incubate for 2 minutes. (18) Engage magnets for bead separation. (19) Incubate for 2 minutes. (20) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1-A1 (4 wells), magnetic bead separation. (volumes 6\u00b5L-200\u00b5L, ~33 min total)",
  "intent": "For this genomic DNA purification, you'll be working with the deep well plate on the magnetic module as your main workspace, the PCR plate in slot 1 as your final destination, and the reservoir in slot 7 for reagents. Start by transferring 30\u00b5L to well A1, mix 5 times at 200\u00b5L volume, then incubate for 20 minutes before adding 50\u00b5L more and mixing 10 times at 50\u00b5L. Add another 6\u00b5L, mix 5 times at 50\u00b5L, then engage the magnets and let the beads separate for 5 minutes before distributing 100\u00b5L to wells A1-A1 across 4 wells and incubating for 1 minute. Continue with the wash steps by transferring 100\u00b5L to A1 and incubating 2 minutes, then disengage magnets, add 30\u00b5L, mix 5 times at 30\u00b5L volume, and incubate 2 minutes before the final magnetic separation for 2 minutes and transferring your purified 30\u00b5L to the final plate.",
